This step is only required if your Ops Manager does not already have the stemcell version required by PAS. For more information about importing stemcells, see [Importing and Managing Stemcells](../opsguide/managing-stemcells.html).

1. Open the [Stemcell product page](https://network.pivotal.io/products/stemcells) in the Pivotal Network.
_Note, you may have to log in._

1. Download the appropriate stemcell version targeted for your IaaS.

1. Navigate to **Stemcell Library** in the **Installation Dashboard**.

1. Click **Import Stemcell** to import the downloaded stemcell <code>.tgz</code> file.

1. When prompted, enable the Ops Manager product checkbox to stage your stemcell.

1. Click **Apply Stemcell to Products**.